First-class.deliveries: 745CricInfo and CricketArchive disagree as to the number of deliveries bowled by Huish. Given that 5-ball overs were standard in England in 1895, the CricketArchive figure of 747 deliveries matches the scorecard data on the same website. The CricInfo data would approximately match if 4 ball overs were standard. The CricketArchive data has been used for deliveries here.
